---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Builds"
  description="Products and projects Carlos Vilhena has built — software, tools, and side quests."
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <header class="mb-8">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-semibold mb-4">Builds</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
        Products and projects I've made over the years. Some are live, some are sold, some are archived — all of them taught me something.
      </p>
    </header>

    <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
      The full grid is coming soon. In the meantime, a few you can poke at: <a href="https://www.boxclock.app/">BoxClock</a>, <a href="https://5minutefrenzy.com/">5 Minute Frenzy</a>, <a href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/astro-recommends">astro-recommends</a>, and the <a href="/about-me/">About</a> page.
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
